<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl mb-6">
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 via-purple-400 to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Installation</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-8">
            Get SoliLang MVC up and running on your machine in minutes.
            Follow these steps to bootstrap your new project.
        </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-400">1</div>
        Prerequisites
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-12">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Rust & Cargo</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Latest stable version</p>
            <code class="text-xs text-indigo-300 mt-2 block">rustc --version</code>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Node.js</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">v16 or higher</p>
            <code class="text-xs text-indigo-300 mt-2 block">node --version</code>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">npm or yarn</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Package manager</p>
            <code class="text-xs text-indigo-300 mt-2 block">npm --version</code>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-400">2</div>
        Install CLI
    </h2>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-gray-950 ring-1 ring-white/10 overflow-hidden shadow-xl mb-12">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-white/5 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-mono">Terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 overflow-x-auto">
<pre><code class="language-bash text-sm"># Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/solilang/solilang.git
cd solilang

# Build the project
cargo build --release

# Install the soli CLI globally
cargo install --path .

# Verify installation
soli --version</code></pre>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-400">3</div>
        Create Project
    </h2>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-gray-950 ring-1 ring-white/10 overflow-hidden shadow-xl mb-12">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-white/5 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-mono">Terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 overflow-x-auto">
<pre><code class="language-bash text-sm"># Clone the MVC example (or create your own)
cd examples/mvc_app

# Install frontend dependencies
npm install

# Build CSS (TailwindCSS)
npm run build:css</code></pre>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-400">4</div>
        Run Server
    </h2>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-gray-950 ring-1 ring-white/10 overflow-hidden shadow-xl mb-6">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-white/5 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-mono">Terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 overflow-x-auto">
<pre><code class="language-bash text-sm"># Start the dev server with hot reload
npm run dev

# Or use the shell script directly
./dev.sh</code></pre>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-8 text-gray-400">
        The server will start at <a href="http://localhost:3000" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300 font-medium">http://localhost:3000</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="my-8 p-4 rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-green-400 font-medium">Hot Reload Enabled</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-green-200/80 mt-1">
                    Edit any file (controllers, middleware, views) and refresh your browser to see changes instantly.
                    No restart needed!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Project Structure</h2>

    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Understanding the layout of a Soli MVC application.</p>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-gray-950 ring-1 ring-white/10 overflow-hidden shadow-xl mb-12">
        <div class="p-4 overflow-x-auto">
<pre><code class="language-text text-sm">my_app/
├── app/
│   ├── controllers/          # Request handlers
│   │   └── *.soli
│   ├── middleware/           # Middleware functions
│   │   ├── auth.soli
│   │   ├── cors.soli
│   │   └── logging.soli
│   ├── models/               # Data models (optional)
│   └── views/                # Templates
│       ├── home/
│       │   └── index.html.erb
│       ├── users/
│       └── layouts/
│           └── application.html.erb
├── config/
│   └── routes.soli           # Route definitions
├── public/                   # Static files
│   ├── css/
│   └── images/
├── package.json              # Node.js config
└── tailwind.config.js        # TailwindCSS config</code></pre>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Building for Production</h2>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-gray-950 ring-1 ring-white/10 overflow-hidden shadow-xl mb-12">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-white/5 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-mono">Terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 overflow-x-auto">
<pre><code class="language-bash text-sm"># Build CSS
npm run build:css

# Build Soli application
cargo build --release

# The compiled binary will be in target/release/soli
./target/release/soli serve .</code></pre>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="my-8 p-4 rounded-xl bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/20">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="text-yellow-400 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-yellow-400 font-medium">Troubleshooting</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-yellow-200/80 mt-1 space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>If CSS doesn't load, run <code>npm run build:css</code></li>
                    <li>If changes don't appear, check the terminal for errors</li>
                    <li>Make sure port 3000 isn't in use by another process</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
